clinicInfoList.emailAppointmentNote:
Preparing For Your Visit:

-Call to reschedule if you develop any symptoms of illness (even if you have had a negative COVID test) or known COVID exposure in the 2 weeks prior to your appointment. Symptoms may include fever, cough, sore throat, loss of taste/smell, diarrhea or body aches.
-Please remove makeup and lotion prior to your visit.
-Bring ID and insurance card(s). You are encouraged to ensure we are in-network with your plan.
-Payment is due at time of appointment for services performed and may include co-pay, co-insurance &/or unmet deductible depending on your plan's benefits.
-If you need to reschedule/cancel, please give 24-hour notice.
-Late patients will kindly be asked to reschedule.

Please visit https://dccderm.com visit for additional details, if needed.

We look forward to taking care of you!
